comment8.text=\n\ Attempts\ to\ move\ to\ an\ adjacent\ room.\n\n\ Rules\:\n\ -\ If\ current\ room\ cleared\:\ can\ move\ to\ any\ neighbor\ room.\n\ -\ If\ not\ cleared\:\ can\ ONLY\ move\ back\ to\ the\ last\ room.\n\n\ @param\ dr\ change\ in\ room\ row\n\ @param\ dc\ change\ in\ room\ col\n
